        <div1 type="body">
            

<p><persName>Merchant</persName>'s License</p>

<p><placeName>Territory of Louisiana   
District of St Genevieve</placeName></p>

<p>This <date when="1806-02-06">sixth day of February one thousand Eight hundred and six</date>
this certifies that <persName>Moses Austin</persName> is authorized to vend merchandize
in this district one year from the present date having this day paid
me <persName>Henry Dodge Sheriff</persName> of the <placeName>district of St Genevieve</placeName> fifteen
Dollars it being the anual tax imposed on the <persName>retailers of 
Merchandize</persName> by a law of this <placeName>territory</placeName>.</p>

<p><persName>H Dodge Sheriff of
the <placeName>district of St Genevieve</placeName></persName></p>

        </div1>
